      name: "Barry Morrow"
    }
    rating: "Pretty Good"
    comments: "The concept is a pretty simple road comedy, but it is more about the relationship between two long-lost brothers; the plot structure is pretty simple as it is about the journey to get from point A to point B, but the climax and exposition feel very dragged out; the character writing is pretty good as you see how gifted Raymond is with his ability and how much Charlie grows to love him as they get to know each other"
  }
